00:35:18.340 --> 00:35:19.760
[laughter]

00:35:19.760 --> 00:35:22.680
By today's standards, not so much. For a nine
year old, I think--.

00:35:22.680 --> 00:35:24.580
&gt;&gt;Jeff: Yeah, that's pretty ambitious, I gotta
tell ya.

00:35:24.580 --> 00:35:30.599
&gt;&gt;Nathan: Well, but I'm pretty ambitious.
So after that, I was a very enthusiastic self-taught

00:35:30.599 --> 00:35:35.730
chef for many years. Finally, while I was
working at Microsoft, I decided to go to chef's

00:35:35.730 --> 00:35:39.690
school in France. So I went to Bill Gates
and I asked him if I could have a leave of

00:35:39.690 --> 00:35:45.040
absence to go to chef's school. This is the
first such, and only, request he's ever gotten.

00:35:45.040 --> 00:35:47.480
&gt;&gt;Jeff: What did he say? I'm just curious.

00:35:47.480 --> 00:35:50.930
&gt;&gt;Nathan: Well, I had enough leverage. I got
