00:35:50.930 --> 00:35:51.930
[laughter]

00:35:51.930 --> 00:35:56.720
But then, in order to go to the chef's school,
they wouldn't take me unless I had work experience.

00:35:56.720 --> 00:36:00.570
So I worked for one night a week at a French
restaurant in Seattle called Rover's.

00:36:00.570 --> 00:36:01.570
&gt;&gt;Jeff: OK.

00:36:01.570 --> 00:36:06.550
&gt;&gt;Nathan: And a very traditional French chef
ran the place. And I'd go at about noon and

00:36:06.550 --> 00:36:11.400
cook all the way through the end of service
and go home. I learned a tremendous amount

00:36:11.400 --> 00:36:18.080
there. In fact, when I eventually went to
chef's school, this one morning we had the

00:36:18.080 --> 00:36:23.940
