00:43:33.920 --> 00:43:36.040
to do the Photoshopping.

00:43:36.040 --> 00:43:42.440
And this guy had just come out of an art school.
He'd just finished his photography thing,

00:43:42.440 --> 00:43:48.080
so not deep experience. But thank God not
deep experience because it allowed us to develop

00:43:48.080 --> 00:43:53.520
a style that was really different and unique,
which is what you see in all these pictures.

00:43:53.520 --> 00:43:56.380
And what they're doing right now is most of
