00:47:50.760 --> 00:47:55.980
What does that really mean? What does a 95
percent confidence interval mean on one of

00:47:55.980 --> 00:48:00.820
those studies? So, one example is some of
the things people say are bad for you, really

00:48:00.820 --> 00:48:07.650
do seem to be bad for you. Trans fats really
